K10D0125_H0127:443b-1: a'arya su warnna n'a ma ma h'a y'a na s'u tra /
K10D0125_H0127:443b-3: 'phags pa gser gyi mdo zhes bya ba theg pa chen po'i mdo /
K10D0125_H0127:443b-5: byang chub sems dpa' thams cad la phyag 'tshal lo //
K10D0125_H0127:443b-6: 'di skad bdag gis thos pa dus gcig na /
K10D0125_H0127:443b-7: bcom ldan 'das rgyal bu rgyal byed kyi tshal mgon
K10D0125_H0127:443b-8: med zas sbyin gyi kun dga' ra ba na bzhugs
K10D0125_H0127:443b-9: te / de'i tshe bcom ldan 'das la tshe dang
K10D0125_H0127:443b-10: ldan pa kun dga' bos 'di skad ces gsol to
K10D0125_H0127:443b-12: byang chub kyi sems ji ltar blta bar bgyi //
K10D0125_H0127:443b-13: bcom ldan 'das kyis bka' stsal pa /
K10D0125_H0127:443b-14: tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bo /
K10D0125_H0127:443b-16: gser dang rang bzhin 'dra bar gnas par blta bar bgyi'o //
K10D0125_H0127:443b-17: gser rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag pa ltar byang
K10D0125_H0127:443b-18: chub kyi sems rang bzhin gyis rnam par dag par
K10D0125_H0127:443b-19: gnas so // mgar bas gser la bzo'i bye brag
K10D0125_H0127:443b-20: tha dad par byas kyang gser rang bzhin mi 'gyur
K10D0125_H0127:443b-21: gnas so // pa ltar / byang chub kyi sems
K10D0125_H0127:443b-22: la yon tan khyad par sna tshogs par snang yang
K10D0125_H0127:443b-23: don dam par byang chub kyi sems las ma g-yos
K10D0125_H0127:443b-24: pas rang bzhin mi 'gyur ba'i phyir ro //
K10D0125_H0127:443b-25: de nas bcom ldan 'das kyis tshigs su bcad de bka' stsal pa /
K10D0125_H0127:443b-26: byang chub sems nyid rnam par dag /
K10D0125_H0127:444a-2: dngos med ngo bo nyid du sgom //
K10D0125_H0127:444a-3: shes rab skye ba'i rgyu la mos //
K10D0125_H0127:444a-4: bcom ldan 'das kyis de skad ces bka' stsal pa dang /
K10D0125_H0127:444a-5: tshe dang ldan pa kun dga' bo dang /
K10D0125_H0127:444a-6: thams cad dang ldan pa'i 'khor de dag dang /
K10D0125_H0127:444a-10: dri zar bcas pa'i 'jig rten yi rang ste bcom
K10D0125_H0127:444a-11: ldan 'das kyis gsungs pa la mngon par bstod do
